-- Compal Electronics to Invest $68 Million in Touch-Panel Supply for Tablets
-- B y   T i m   C u l p a n
-- 2010-12-29T07:28:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-29/compal-electronics-to-spend-nt-2-billion-in-touch-panel-supply-for-tablets.html
Compal Electronics Inc. will invest
NT$2 billion to make capacitive touch panels to boost
competitiveness and reduce product design times for tablet
devices, the Taipei-based company said in an exchange filing.  Compal will invest in HengHao Technology Co. with NT$1.4
billion of the funds used to buy so-called 4.5-generation color
filter facilities and equipment from Chunghwa Picture Tubes
Ltd., it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tim Culpan in Taipei at 
